name: Senior #11 - Matthijs
description:
Matthijs is a 67-year-old former government spy who enjoys sewing, going to the movies and brewing tea. He is quiet and resilient, but can also be very intimidating and a bit deranged.

Matthijs’s best friend is a former K-pop idol called Ji-yong. They get on well most of the time. They’re currently learning how to make NFTs together.
